      "text": [
        "3540 - وَ قَالَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : فِي رَجُلٍ أَخَذَ آبِقاً فَفَرَّ مِنْهُ قَالَ \"لَيْسَ عَلَيْهِ شَيْءٌ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3540 - Imam (as) said regarding a man who captured a runaway slave and then the slave escaped from him:\n\"There is nothing (no liability) upon him.\""
        ]
      }
    }
  },
